{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01KfEVp49FXGUv77ZeSPdiaP","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have all the information I need to provide a comprehensive report.\n\n## Bounded Contexts Architecture Review\n\n### Summary\nAll 7 required bounded contexts exist in `/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/` with proper ports/adapters separation. The `adapters/` directory contains comprehensive side-effect implementations.\n\n---\n\n### 1. Contexts Status\n\n#### Existing Contexts:\nAll required contexts are present:\n\n1. **contexts/workspace_governance/**\n   - Files: `config.rs`, `mod.rs`\n   - Status: Exists\n   - Port/Adapter: Uses `FileSystem` adapter from `adapters/fs.rs` via dependency injection\n\n2. **contexts/project_run_record/**\n   - Files: `journal.rs`, `model.rs`, `service.rs`, `queries.rs`, `mod.rs`\n   - Status: Exists with comprehensive ports\n   - Ports (15 total):\n     - `ProjectStorePort`\n     - `JournalStorePort`\n     - `ArtifactStorePort`\n     - `RuntimeLogStorePort`\n     - `RunSnapshotPort` / `RunSnapshotWritePort`\n     - `RollbackPointStorePort`\n     - `RepositoryResetPort`\n     - `PayloadArtifactWritePort`\n     - `RuntimeLogWritePort`\n     - `AmendmentQueuePort`\n     - `ActiveProjectPort`\n\n3. **contexts/workflow_composition/**\n   - Files: `contracts.rs`, `engine.rs`, `payloads.rs`, `renderers.rs`, `retry_policy.rs`, `mod.rs`\n   - Status: Exists\n   - Port/Adapter: No explicit port traits (orchestration logic contained within context)\n   - Note: Uses flow definitions and validation profiles without external port abstractions\n\n4. **contexts/agent_execution/**\n   - Files: `model.rs`, `service.rs`, `session.rs`, `mod.rs`\n   - Status: Exists with ports\n   - Ports (3 total):\n     - `AgentExecutionPort`\n     - `RawOutputPort`\n     - `SessionStorePort`\n\n5. **contexts/requirements_drafting/**\n   - Files: `contracts.rs`, `model.rs`, `re